  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Point-Data FB:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> they can measure the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">motion-values</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> of any Point in the model. The Point might be a start-Point, End-Point, center-Point or Motion-Point along a sketch-path.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Measurement FB:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> can measure the motion-values between Points and Lines.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The motion-values at the output-connectors can be plotted with a Graph FB or used as independent variable at the input to a different FB.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">See also: </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-FB-Point-Data" styleclass="T_Menusmall" translate="true">Add Point-Data FB</link><text styleclass="T_Menusmall" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-FB-Measurement" styleclass="T_Menusmall" translate="true">Measurement FB</link><text styleclass="T_Menusmall" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-FB-Motion" styleclass="T_Menusmall" translate="true">Motion FB</link></para>
